model.agent.humanAgent.tacticalLevel.navigation.pathfinder

Class PathFinder

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.agent.humanAgent.tacticalLevel.navigation.pathfinder.PathFinder
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AStarPathFinder, DijkstraPathFinder, JumpPointSearchPathFinder

    public abstract class PathFinder
extends java.lang.Object
    A path finder finds a feasible path between a specified starting Position and goal Position on a specified Map. A path is represented as a List of Positions, where each Position is a corner point in the path. If no feasible path can be found, a list containing only the goal position Position is returned.
    Author:
    S.A.M. Janssen
